prompts.user_template:
Evaluate the following copy against the provided personas and commercials. Then produce outputs per output_schema.

COPY:
{{copy.content}}

CONTEXT:
{{copy.context_notes}}

PERSONAS:
Primary: {{personas.primary_persona}}
Secondary: {{personas.secondary_personas}}
Industry: {{personas.industry}} | Size: {{personas.company_size}} | Region: {{personas.region}}

COMMERCIALS:
Avg deal size: ${{commercials.avg_deal_size}}
Qualified pipeline (90d): ${{commercials.qualified_pipeline_90d}}
Baseline win rate: {{commercials.baseline_win_rate}}
Sales cycle: {{commercials.sales_cycle_days}} days
Risk tolerance: {{commercials.deployment_risk_tolerance}}
